Value Required zone_name (\S+)
Value priority (\d+)
Value interface (\S+)
Value action (deny|permit)
Value description (\S+.*)

Start
  ^\s*security-zone\s+${zone_name}\s+priority\s+${priority} -> Record
  ^\s*security-zone\s+${zone_name}\s+interface\s+${interface} -> Record
  ^\s*security-zone\s+${zone_name}\s+inner-zone-action\s+${action} -> Record
  ^\s*security-zone\s+${zone_name}\s+description\s+${description}$$ -> Record
  ^\s*$$